                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2011-08-12</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">╮(￣▽￣&#34;)╭</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

